data.description: PRICED TO SALE! Newly built 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath with 2-car garage home near Turtle Run Park. The home was efficiently designed with both a living room and family room. There is plenty of space for the new homeowner to extend the back patio and enclose it. There is also plenty of space in the back yard for pets and children to play, secured by a tall wooden fence. Each bedroom and bathroom were designed and laid in a fashion to take advantage of natural lighting. The kitchen was efficiently designed with a long island/high-top design. Also, with plenty of space for a dining room table. Great area near restaurants, shopping centers and good schools.
